  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b89\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd : \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bc2\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "My father is fine: Don't spread fake news and provoke people - Naamal",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Fake news has been spread that I am related to a Qatari company and that my father former Prime Minister Mahinda Rajapaksa has been admitted to the hospital due to ill health.",
        "Member of Parliament Namal Rajapaksa said that he would request everyone not to spread such fake news and try to incite people amid the crises the country is facing.",
        "He said this at a press conference held on Monday (04) at the Podujana Peramuna headquarters in Bhattaramulla and further mentioned,",
        "Namal Rajapaksa is one of the members of the board of directors of a company in Qatar.",
        "Neither I nor my family have anything to do with the said company. The said Qatari company clarified about the person named Namal Rajapaksa.",
        "So I request you not to try to incite people by spreading such fake news without verifying the facts.",
        "Similarly, a fake news was shared that my father former Prime Minister Mahinda Rajapaksa was admitted to the hospital due to ill health. There is no defect in his health. He is in good health.",
        "I also request you to refrain from publishing such news in relation to us."
      ],
